Colette Descombes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Colette_Descombes 0 Colette Descombes is a French film actress, active between 1961 and 1978. If she was of legal age (18) in 1961, she was probably born circa 1943, but her birthdate is nowhere on the internet. Descombes made her film debut in Les nymphettes, a French drama directed by Henri Zaphiratos in which she had the main role, then starred with some regularity in Italian, French and Spanish productions.
